      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owners. The engine starts reliably and runs smoothly, while the transmission shifts as expected for a vehicle of this age. The interior is clean with only minor signs of regular use, and the exterior paint retains a nice luster despite a few small, typical stone chips. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a solid, road-ready car that has many miles left to offer.",
